description: Demolition of the Red House and community hall and the retention and refurbishment, alteration and conversion of the Grade II White House, Church, Courtyard block and gatehouse and erection of 14 two, three four and five storey blocks to provide 30 bed care home, 38 assisted living flats and 82 extra care flats and houses, 2 guest suites, 3 carer stations and 11 key worker units (total 166 units), a plant block and associated parking and landscaping.
